member.name: T:Xamarin.Forms.Labs.Sample.iOS.AppDelegate
member.remarks: The UIApplicationDelegate for the application. This class is responsible for launching the User Interface of the application, as well as listening (and optionally responding) to application events from iOS.

member.name: M:Xamarin.Forms.Labs.Sample.iOS.AppDelegate.FinishedLaunching(MonoTouch.UIKit.UIApplication,MonoTouch.Foundation.NSDictionary)
member.remarks: This method is invoked when the application has loaded and is ready to run. In this method you should instantiate the window, load the UI into it and then make the window visible. You have 17 seconds to return from this method, or iOS will terminate your application.
